  "identifier": "review",
  "description": "Provides a tidy relational algebra for iterative semantic review of tabular data. The package creates reviewable claims from ordinary data frames, allocates successive review rounds, records provenance for each review, and finalises reviewed values while preserving review history. It supports reproducible review workflows that remain compatible with ordinary data frames and metadata packages such as 'dataset'.",
